				"our name in the description and other text, provided that you don’t promote your products using our " +
				"name."
		},
		new()
		{
			IconClass = "fa-solid fa-brain",
			Title = "AI Usage",
			Description =
				"Today's technology is mostly focused on artificial intelligence (AI), which makes people's lives " +
				"much easier. We have seen how important AI is in today's life. However, we've also seen concerns " +
